2026-05-14T06:23:36.2731566Z 223        <!--
2026-05-14T06:23:36.2732136Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-14T06:23:36.2733314Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-14T06:23:36.2734179Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-14T06:23:36.2734996Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-14T06:23:36.2735702Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
